<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000601/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Professors will ask students to complete individual or group theoretical and practical assignments (as shown in the table Assessment activities above), which will be graded. The obtained scores will be combined to obtain the final grade of the course.
A score of 5/10 is required to pass the course. If any student obtains a grade lower than the mimum required in a given part, they can recover said part in an exceptional call in January and finally in July."""@es .

